{"type":"message","id":"c5086066","parentId":"f9c84f20","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:25:49.491Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Installed — the missing tools are in place now.\n\nWhat’s done:\n- `gcloud` installed\n- `gog` installed\n- verified both work\n\nWhat’s **still blocking full Gmail access**:\nI still need your **Google OAuth client credentials** for `gog`, and then you’ll need to do a one-time Google authorization.\n\n**Simplest next step:**\n1. Go to Google Cloud Console\n2. Create/download a **Desktop app OAuth client JSON**\n3. Send me that **JSON file**\n\nIf you want, I can walk you through it step by step, very simply.  \nReply:\n\n**guide me**\n\nand I’ll give you the exact clicks.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc0daedcc8191814bdc85c373eb5d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":184,"output":144,"cacheRead":76032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76360,"cost":{"input":0.00046,"output":0.00216,"cacheRead":0.019008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021628}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777123545267,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc0d99e1881919f6932d9205b1eb5"}}
