{"type":"message","id":"2b030a0b","parentId":"ed8c9df2","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:34:14.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That’s the blocker — **Gmail API isn’t enabled yet** for your Google project.\n\nDo this:\n\n1. Open this link:  \n   https://console.developers.google.com/apis/api/gmail.googleapis.com/overview?project=297911594147\n\n2. Click **Enable**\n\n3. Wait about **1–5 minutes**\n\n4. Run again:\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail labels list\n```\n\nIf it works after that, send me the result and I’ll help you finish the next step.\n\nIf you want, after enabling it I can also help you test:\n- unread inbox listing\n- important email triage\n- safer read-only mail workflow","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc2d386408191a9a18fffb26a5084\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":694,"output":149,"cacheRead":79616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80459,"cost":{"input":0.0017350000000000002,"output":0.002235,"cacheRead":0.019903999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023874}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124049349,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc2d1ae448191b0ff1231f5a5afad"}}
