{"type":"message","id":"542ac714","parentId":"1be3fdad","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:35:50.783Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread in:inbox\" --limit 20\n```\n\nIf you want a cleaner priority view, use:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread in:inbox category:primary\" --limit 20\n```\n\nAnd for **important unread only**:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread is:important in:inbox\" --limit 20\n```\n\nIf you paste the result here, I can sort them into:\n- urgent\n- reply soon\n- low priority\n- ignore","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc333d21c819189f0636d3142c8d3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":460,"output":162,"cacheRead":80640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81262,"cost":{"input":0.0011500000000000002,"output":0.00243,"cacheRead":0.020159999999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023739999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124145095,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc33172008191b1410f15fdd53451"}}
