{"type":"message","id":"850d041e","parentId":"8a75f155","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:36:00.551Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this one:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread is:important in:inbox\" --limit 20\n```\n\nIf you want, make it shorter with an alias:\n\n```bash\nalias gmail-important='gog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread is:important in:inbox\" --limit 20'\n```\n\nThen just run:\n\n```bash\ngmail-important\n```\n\nIf you want, I can also give you:\n- `gmail-unread`\n- `gmail-primary`\n- `gmail-today`\n- `gmail-needs-reply`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc33de2608191a8db3b201573dec6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":245,"output":146,"cacheRead":81152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81543,"cost":{"input":0.0006125000000000001,"output":0.00219,"cacheRead":0.020288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0230905}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124156520,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc33cd8e08191a8eb230bac7f38c4"}}
