{"type":"message","id":"926ac67e","parentId":"fff7fa81","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:36:25.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use:\n\n```bash\nalias gmail-unread='gog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail threads list --query \"is:unread in:inbox\" --limit 20'\n```\n\nThen run:\n\n```bash\ngmail-unread\n```\n\nIf you want, I can give you the full little set next:\n- `gmail-unread`\n- `gmail-important`\n- `gmail-primary`\n- `gmail-today`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc3578d6481919f09d4121fa9c807\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":264,"output":94,"cacheRead":81408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81766,"cost":{"input":0.0006600000000000001,"output":0.00141,"cacheRead":0.020352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.022421999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124181990,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc35650248191bf5c7ce8456e875c"}}
