o the **gateway process**:\n\n```bash\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='your-keyring-password'\n```\n\nThen restart OpenClaw:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nAfter that, I should be able to check Gmail from chat.\n\n**Recommended way**\nRun these on the same machine/account that runs OpenClaw:\n\n```bash\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='your-keyring-password'\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nThen come back here and say:\n\n**check unread gmail**\n\nand I’ll test it.\n\n**Important:**  \nDon’t send me the password in chat. Set it locally on your machine.\n\nIf you want it to survive terminal restarts, I can help you do the **persistent version** next for:\n- **Codespaces**\n- **Linux server**\n- **macOS**\n- **Docker**\n\nTell me which one you’re using.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc3db9d608191ba1bebbf72ade88d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":304,"output":491,"cacheRead":85120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85915,"cost":{"input":0.00076,"output":0.007365,"cacheRead":0.02128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029405}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124307475,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc3d3cdf88191b1f60474afb4ede4"}}
