{"type":"message","id":"4d914873","parentId":"f8dc9b4e","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:40:47.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc45bb83c81919e58b3524a722fa3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp7MRc0VHhNEEr4LGXT5sW-FS6bsieN9yuxMPNW95nKggkb22RDEw8-kRUDrIBALBKyWeIRKTSKvTZe45ZWwI1EMd3DOWx4xz2nI-MaHD4XAmuC6--SGG11HZ0vevgp-miu1q87yO7l8qUGUQcREUag0-D57qAiYC1ey5hE6lVYFftOJN6NxUlc0qyc9SZGJOlhNorFDCi6ihIG4Iuui5RAIWrGljc9Z-qlWCFbuZJRVe6LTKxXqZFuPi-PdiK0x_pXTGartC0zMWZ9SY4GjJrWlZkhJ7_B4jQiKCSDR8-wq646sfqgioZ3a59yTE3LtheO3BfL19YvTbamogJ33m7v6GU1MYou2-n0lABKrSCCgGX02GMExDKdwYMUU8DQ8zCtO1OAfVezBcemVVm011CiM4L3-CuokfTVJLtR5vNsSdW4fTCLaKL8wZpbS84NbKaEDOEoaAQ8FR3vlYo7ybzJG7P8D4qL1b-f1DsRUSASVZXguBXqbB38e3dENazuvZWv1Pp6hN79ES48zIQp6L4Th4ffxj6pMQ64obTshvaMZY7b_r5WdnD2K-seeQSfrRDO9HjFDiwkaB9B9R_EtwnBjtke3z88CKDvEDazqg0KAz5IV8K32Nw7kX8t64Vyt47ckWqOGVCaYjhJFVfLdazKptIWkpymG9JwcKzaJvmWrYBkUWY2xmrTKnGYyCfcBMeZLUHxUopFSdpO43lAZwdun64gYPneEtguw4s6M9-qOxIIej_-0nmgSz9X4lCUmKO0iW-DYgFVjMAWYUTPI1xRNYmhQ4iFOWrFI7bG7REgTM6nnPZyg1dJphTJm_9jM6kcs5eXi-ZLAp_CC-eU9neSJhAlju9PsG4IOWs534wZonZYrwayqRM9oj7JXrrqe2GRzZSFfWDT3SxklQDJj7LXO77OFmDZk2wsrW_H7OIHV6pcJRO_xqhBij353wdbgFSOrfD\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"You **choose it yourself** — it’s not something Google gives you.\n\nIt’s just a **local encryption password** used by `gog` to unlock the Gmail token saved on your machine.\n\nExample:\n\n```bash\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='my-strong-random-password-123'\n```\n\nBetter example:\n- long\n- hard to guess\n- only you know it\n\nFor example:\n\n```bash\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='Moth-gmail-vault-92!blue-lantern'\n```\n\nThen use the **same exact password** every time on that machine, because it’s what unlocks the stored token.\n\nSo the flow is:\n\n1. **Pick a password yourself**\n2. Run:\n```bash\nexport GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='the-password-you-chose'\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nIf you want, I can help you do it **properly and persistently** so you don’t need to type it every time.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc45c49748191acf23b08ae398c50\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1171,"output":219,"cacheRead":84608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85998,"cost":{"input":0.0029275000000000004,"output":0.003285,"cacheRead":0.021152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0273645}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124441809,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc45a3edc8191b6e6aa1da2d8843f"}}
