me-password-you-chose'\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nThen tell me:\n\n**check unread gmail**\n\nAnd I’ll test again.\n\nIf you want, I can help you make it **persistent** properly — tell me which setup you use:\n- **GitHub Codespaces**\n- **Linux server**\n- **macOS**\n- **Docker**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc68ab8f481918f690c8431b7d919\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":165,"output":234,"cacheRead":86144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86543,"cost":{"input":0.00041250000000000005,"output":0.00351,"cacheRead":0.021536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0254585}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777124996442,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc684e62881918fc7ec0808888143"}}
