{"type":"message","id":"59b9a5bd","parentId":"85ea118d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T13:50:50.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect — for **GitHub Codespaces**, the clean way is to make it persistent in your shell startup.\n\nRun:\n\n```bash\necho \"export GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD='your-chosen-password'\" >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nThen verify:\n\n```bash\necho $GOG_KEYRING_PASSWORD\n```\n\nAfter that, tell me:\n\n**check unread gmail**\n\nand I’ll test it from chat.\n\nIf you want a slightly safer version, I can also show you how to store it in **Codespaces Secrets** instead of writing it directly into `~/.bashrc`.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc6b8133081919c153f53577572cf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":564,"output":135,"cacheRead":86016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86715,"cost":{"input":0.00141,"output":0.002025,"cacheRead":0.021504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024939}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777125046310,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecc6b6c4c881919e688491241d4fcd"}}
