{"type":"message","id":"8f756b1e","parentId":"4148641b","timestamp":"2026-04-25T14:05:16.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Yep — the problem is you pasted the **command** there instead of the **redirect URL**.\n\nWhen it says:\n\n`Paste redirect URL (Enter or Ctrl-D):`\n\nyou must paste something that looks like this:\n\n```text\nhttp://127.0.0.1:37365/oauth2/callback?state=...&code=...\n```\n\nNot this:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail labels list\n```\n\nSo do it again:\n\n```bash\ngog auth add xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx --services gmail --readonly --gmail-scope readonly --gmail-no-send --manual\n```\n\nThen:\n1. open the Google link it prints\n2. approve access\n3. copy the **full redirect URL** from the browser address bar\n4. paste that URL into the terminal prompt\n\nOnly **after that finishes successfully**, run:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail labels list\n```\n\nIf you want, after you get the redirect URL, paste it **here first** and I’ll check if it looks correct before you put it into the terminal.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecca1825308191b52a1525c94e9134\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":688,"output":238,"cacheRead":89472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90398,"cost":{"input":0.0017200000000000002,"output":0.0035700000000000003,"cacheRead":0.022368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027658}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777125909713,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecca163bcc8191bc3de9bea3cf52b1"}}
