{"type":"message","id":"57d98710","parentId":"b7956104","timestamp":"2026-04-25T14:06:45.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Still not working yet.\n\nThe Gmail token still isn’t usable from the chat runtime, so the reconnect likely **didn’t finish successfully**.\n\nMost likely blocker:\n- the OAuth paste step failed again, or\n- the token was stored in a shell session but not usable by this runtime\n\nFastest way to confirm:\nrun this in your terminal:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail labels list\n```\n\nIf that works, then run:\n\n```bash\ngog --account xxx_YOUR_EMAIL_xxx gmail search 'is:unread in:inbox'\n```\n\nPaste the output here and I’ll sort it for you right away.\n\nIf `gog gmail labels list` does **not** work yet, then Gmail auth is still incomplete and we need to redo the auth step carefully.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0e249c009ade638f0169ecca72b51c8191b0d9d74d9a653a54\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":171,"output":173,"cacheRead":90496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90840,"cost":{"input":0.00042750000000000004,"output":0.002595,"cacheRead":0.022624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0256465}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777126000869,"responseId":"resp_0e249c009ade638f0169ecca7152148191aed8075d797c1be7"}}
